data.description: Spacious & well kept, this charming home features 4 bedroom, 2 baths, 2 living spaces and a 2 car garage with RV parking. Vaulted ceilings, ceiling fans, new windows and exterior doors! New roof in 2019 plus gutters and soffits, kitchen cabinets, hot water heater, air conditioner, and new poured RV pad. Enjoy the relaxing back yard and patio. Darla Jean park in just a few blocks away. Come see this gem!
